com.qualitestgroup.kdt.keywords.common

Class Browser.Launch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualitestgroup.kdt.framework.Keyword
      • com.qualitestgroup.kdt.keywords.common.Browser.Launch
  • Enclosing class:
    Browser

    public class Browser.Launch
extends Keyword
    Opens a web browser.

    Arguments:

    • Browser: The browser to open. Accepted values are [IE, Chrome, Firefox, Edge, PhantomJS, Safari].
    • Timeout: Sets the maximum timeout (in seconds) for locating an element (Default 30).
    • BrowserVersion: The desired version of the browser. Other accepted values are "any" for any version, and "latest" for the latest version. (Defaults to "latest")
    • Platform: Operating system to run on. (Defaults to Windows 7)
    • 64Bit: Whether to request a 64-bit OS. (Default to false)
    • LaunchTimeout: Timeout in minutes to open a browser over Selenium Grid. (Defaults to 5)
    • IsMobile: If this is a mobile web browser. Only works for Chrome and Safari.
    • MobilePlatformVersion: Version of the mobile OS
    • MobileDeviceName: Name of the mobile device
